        <div class="def-box" style="margin: 0;">
            <p><strong>âœ“ RosnÄ…cy:</strong> a<sub>n+1</sub> âˆ’ a<sub>n</sub> &gt; 0</p>
            <p><strong>âœ“ MalejÄ…cy:</strong> a<sub>n+1</sub> âˆ’ a<sub>n</sub> &lt; 0</p>
